d\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"the outcome\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 555}, {\"ngram\": \"team-mate Chiles' bronze\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 600}, {\"ngram\": \"tribute\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 617}, {\"ngram\": \"the most iconic images\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The vast majority of fans praised Biles and Chiles for their sportsmanship but Baltimore Ravens cornerback Marlon Humphrey bizarrely called it 'disgusting'.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 859, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 782, \"end\": 798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baltimore_Ravens\", \"score\": 0.999999932772655, \"rank\": 4.286343703643624e-08, \"text\": \"Baltimore Ravens\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baltimore_Ravens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baltimore_Ravens\"}, {\"begin\": 810, \"end\": 825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marlon_Humphrey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marlon Humphrey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marlon_Humphrey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marlon_Humphrey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The vast majority\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 742}, {\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 753}, {\"ngram\": \"their sportsmanship\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This is literally disgusting,' the 28-year-old posted on X, before adding: 'I am lowkey getting cooked right now.\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I am getting cussed out in Brazilian on Instagram lol.'\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 1039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1024, \"end\": 1033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0053196715794678e-24, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brazilian\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking onNBC's TODAYshow, Biles defended the gesture and said it was important for the Americans to give Andrade her 'flowers'.\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1148, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999974989, \"rank\": 2.0455575279572525e-12, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Speaking onNBC's TODAYshow\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"the gesture\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1095}, {\"ngram\": \"the Americans\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"flowers\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is everything.pic.twitter.com/FrXz7wWtQg 'I think it's all about sportsmanship, and we do not care whether we win or lose,' the 11-time Olympic medal winner said.\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1340, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sportsmanship\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"the 11-time Olympic medal winner\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We are always going to keep a good face and support our competitors because they have worked just as hard as we have for that moment.\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good face\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"our competitors\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So you have to give them their flowers.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their flowers\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's exactly what me and Jordan were doing, and we were so happy for her.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1550, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\", \"score\": 0.8562038914213778, \"rank\": 0.09755623034182796, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She deserved it.\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She had the best floor routine of the day and in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best floor routine\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1659}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's like, yeah, she deserved it.'\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a separate interview, Biles described Andrade as a 'queen' and said it was 'super-exciting' to be a part of the first all-black podium in men or women's gymnastics at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1761, \"end\": 1768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999974989, \"rank\": 2.0455575279572525e-12, \"text\": \"